725561f-b.title: Queens: 66th Avenue - Alderton Street
725561f-b.text:
~Sixty-sixth Avenue (WRite Pot Road) north side, in line of Alderton Street, showing in three views the Springsteen house. Michael S. Srpingsteen (b.1804 d. 1886) erected this house in 1859. His son Dueid who married Anna W. Monfort of Brooklyn inherited it. He died ahout 1912. His widow sold
it in 1928.
May 1923
View 2: April 1923
View 3: July 1923
Eumene L. Armhruster Collection
